relatedBlades.title: Optimize your website for a better UX
relatedBlades.subtitle: Supercharge your web application delivery with the world's fastest network
relatedBlades.copy: Cloudflare's application delivery services puts your website within milliseconds of nearly every Internet user, helping you easily diagnose UX issues, optimize caching, and accelerate dynamic content delivery.

columnContent.title: Faster performance
columnContent.description: Cloudflare's global network caches your static content 50 ms of %{GlobalInternetConnectedPercent}% of all Internet users. And our smart routing guides dynamic content over the fastest Internet paths.

columnContent.title: Better reliability
columnContent.description: Cloudflare's anycast networking — with network locations in over %{DataCenterCount} cities — ensures your users can always access your content.

columnContent.title: Simpler management
columnContent.description: Cloudflare services are all built to work together out of the box, and are available via an easy-to-use single pane of glass.

relatedBlades.title: Cloudflare optimizes every aspect of website delivery
relatedBlades.copy:
__Diagnose UX issues__
Cloudflare Browser Insights lets you measure performance metrics from the perspective of visitors all over the globe. Our Speed Page tool also generates snapshots of your loading process. And Cloudflare Observatory uses synthetic tests and user data to optimize web performance. __Speed up content delivery__
Our industry-leading DNS and content delivery network (CDN) work together automatically to accept requests and serve content from our %{DataCenterCount}-city network. In addition, our Argo Smart Routing uses Cloudflare network intelligence to steer dynamic content over the fastest Internet paths. __Simplify media delivery and management__
Cloudflare Image Optimization and Stream make media delivery seamless. Create bespoke image variants from primary one, optimize mobile images, and deliver live and on-demand video.

relatedBlades.htmlContent: Picsart uses Cloudflare to accelerate image delivery

content.value: Picsart, a photo editing application provider, anticipated content delivery challenges as their growth outpaced their server capacity.

Thinking proactively, they adopted Cloudflare's content delivery network. Now, their web assets are being cached and delivered by a powerful %{DataCenterCount}-city network drawing on industry-leading network intelligence.
With Cloudflare, the load time of our images improved by 2-3x. And on top of that, we're saving over 50% on our monthly bandwidth usage

planFeatures.name: Load Balancing
planFeatures.description:
Price includes a base fee plus usage fees. Usage fee is determined by the number of DNS requests made by visitors.

###### Base Fee
*Free, Pro, and Business Plan pricing:* - Up to 2 origin servers: $5 per month - Additional origins, up to 20: $5 per month per origin *Enterprise customers:* - Custom Pricing ---
###### Usage-based Fees
*Free, Pro, and Business Plan pricing:* - First 500k DNS requests are free - $0.50 per every 500k DNS requests after *Enterprise customers:* Can negotiate a reduced rate through custom pricing.
